README                       -1-            WikiTeX 2.0-beta





                  WikiTeX 2.0-beta README

          Peter Danenberg <pcd at wikitex dot org>
                   http://wikisophia.org


0.  Prerequisites

     o    PHP 5.2+ compiled with curl and xmlrpc

     o    MediaWiki 1.6+

     o    mod_tex 0.1[1]

1.  Installation

     1.   Copy ../wikitex to MEDIAWIKI/extensions.

     2.   Copy config/default.php to config/local.php;  edit
          local.php.

     3.   Add the following line to LocalSettings.php:

          include_once("$IP/extensions/wikitex/main.php");

2.  Copyright

     WikiTeX: expansible mod_tex client for MediaWiki
